    <PrimAttribute name="cashValue" id="815fd78c-8491-4cb6-81ec-c42bf452aa6c">
        <precision>23</precision>
        <scaleFactor>6</scaleFactor>
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Decimal"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>The cash receipt, credit or payment value.


The cash receipt cashValue includes tax, includes rounding, includes applied credits
The cash payment cash value does not include tax, does not include applied credit, there is no cash payment for a receipt rounding amount.

If a cargo is merged it's cash payments are voided, the cash value is unchanged; but it is linked to a zombie.
If an invoice line is voided the cash payments on it are voided, the cash value is unchanged.
</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="dateTime" id="9595a685-6b9e-4509-b416-5ff9c314bf34">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="TimeStamp"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>The date that the cash receipt, payment or credit was created.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
